{"tid":972005,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千億礦權案　拍片自保法官傳失聯","createTime":"2019-01-07T05:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T07:12:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1904ab163a5fa4710ea300f9f5f705caaea083a4","tid":972005,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:36:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190107/20585508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190107%2F20585508&d=CLvBSNi7HEDZp085ZmrW7sKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=32dac4d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190107%2F20585508&h=aca1906b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190107/20585508</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月07日 <br />\n<br />\n千億礦權案　拍片自保法官傳失聯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190107/large/a1805a3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190107%2Flarge%2Fa1805a3.gif&h=94b5f341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n央視前主持崔永元揭露「陝西千億礦權案」的二審法庭文件失蹤案，矛頭直指最高法院有內鬼，事件涉及層級更上至最高法院院長周強。崔永元更公佈，文件顯示周曾作出干預審判指示。昨天，為自保爆料並拍攝自白短片的法官王林清（圖）被傳已失聯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳最高院院長曾干預<br />\n<br />\n崔永元昨再公佈一段疑似王林清的自白短片，片中王林清敍述了其分管領導杜萬華與周強干預審判的細節。對於合議庭的一致的礦權歸屬意見，杜萬華對王林清施壓要求重審：「儘管你們合議庭意見一致，但鑑於這案件的關注度高，而且，背後的利益很大&hellip;&hellip;不能因你們合議庭一致意見就這麼定了。」其後更稱「周院長（應為周強）有明確指示，要發回重審」，但王林清表示這行為違反民事訴訟法，杜萬華則命令「你保留個人意見，趕緊回去合議」。<br />\n<br />\n在崔公佈的一份「民一終字第81號」案件判決書的批示文件，其中杜萬華在2017年11月23日的批示中提及判決書做了三次修改並請周院長批示。在12月18日的補充批示中，杜萬華寫到「本案判決書周強院長已經審核，請即發」。<br />\n<br />\n《財新》引述接近王林清的人士稱，王於1月3日曾露面，之後被帶到最高法院附近一家賓館接受最高法院調查組訊問，家屬對該調查方向感擔憂。2018年12月30日凌晨首段短片披露，王林清曾對一些朋友做了簡單回應，稱自己性格不適合體制。崔永元昨晚再發微博：「王林清，請馬上聯繫我，我要確定你安全。」暗示王或已失聯。<br />\n<br />\n財新/微博  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n美媒詳列五大武器　大陸攻台軍備趨「致命」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n加議員訪華　或討論公民被拘事件"},{"pid":"2f6d665979bda045a07f8daf94ba0cc50960ac79","tid":972005,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:43:03.000Z","msg":"仲邊有得傾<br />\n學人講法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b6ad3e742234b336b2cca0742120e5b39a46535","tid":972005,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T06:18:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放心啦，拍得片唔會死得，實有排在生既！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支那文化有樣偉大發明叫&quot;淩遲&quot;架！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"faa3c6d86263072e23bc9f2778df7f324a680c7f","tid":972005,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"拍左片就唔會有抑鬱？"},{"pid":"ad7b8a3f11939af90eab40ea565e8fd950abd931","tid":972005,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"尋晚聽仁哥講呢單野,好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mXMRvgOGSWg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmXMRvgOGSWg&d=CLvBSNi7HEDZp085ZmrW7sKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=f6d7c0af\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mXMRvgOGSWg</a>"},{"pid":"230c90da30f8b159d2c196706182bffe5f1f78d8","tid":972005,"uid":13492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T07:12:50.000Z","msg":"被失蹤<br />\n被旅遊<br />\n被報平安<br />\n共党滅口三步曲"}]}